Class MapRpcServer

java.lang.Object
com.rabbitmq.client.RpcServer
com.rabbitmq.client.MapRpcServer
public class MapRpcServer extends RpcServer
Subclass of RpcServer which uses AMQP wire-format encoded tables as requests and replies.
